room_title: Escape room "Escape the X Corporation" by Amazing Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_description:
You thought volunteering to be part of an experimental program with the mysterious X Corporation would be a fun idea. All you had to do was try their experimental drug X7 and you would be handsomely paid for your time! What’s the worst that could happen?
The next thing you know, you have woken up in a bizarre room with a group of strangers. None of you have any idea what is happening or how you became trapped in the strange room... A timer is counting down from one hour and signs tell you to “continue the test.”
